This modern spacious family home is tucked away in a sought after location, with the benefits of estate living, privacy, security and spacious rooms. The living rooms are light and opens out to the central sun-drenched pool courtyard. Designed with style and function in mind, the double-story residence provides 3 bedrooms, en suite bathrooms, study, extra room that can be converted in 4rth bedroom, extra storerooms, braai room, a modern fitted kitchen, gas stove, marble finishes, with scullery/laundry. Its scale and appearance differentiates this house from other houses and residences in the surrounding areas. Extras include: Decked and covered patio, infinity pool, low maintenance established garden landscaped, irrigation system, over-sized garage and domestic facilities.      